entries.title_d: Search for lost refugee transports. We will provide you with waypoints to possible locations. Follow them and keep your eyes peeled. When you complete this mission, return to Captain Kreezo in Tyrena for your next assignment.
entries.title: Corellia system: Search for lost refugee transports.
entries.split_quest_alert: Our sensors have picked up one of the transports! Stand by for orders.
entries.quest_patrol_d: Waypoints of the search route will be provided to your nav computer.
entries.quest_patrol3_d: Fly to this nav point and continue your search for a lost refugee transport
entries.quest_patrol2_d: Continue your search for a lost refugee transport at this nav point.
entries.quest_patrol1_d: Fly to this navigation point in earch of a lost refugee transport.
entries.quest_location_d: The Corellia system is fairly safe from Imperial contact but you can't relax, the Empire is not non existant and pirates can be found anywhere in the galaxy.
